    "jei.cosmicsafari.divflame_feather_jei": "a greasy feather that occasionally is molted from the diva-like divflame",
    "jei.cosmicsafari.dna_machine_jei_infor": "This amazing machine turns raw cosmic DNA into a fully formed creature inside of a capsule. It requires 3 of the same DNA, a capsule, and some cosmite",
    "jei.cosmicsafari.feeding_info": "This block will automatically feed certain items to Cosmos animals. When they eat food, Cosmos animals produce a strange material known as vinyl. Different creatures produce different types of vinyl. You can also feed creatures by right clicking them with their favorite food.",
    "jei.cosmicsafari.floral_vinyl_jei_info": "A type of leaf that resembles vinyl. You can occasionally find it growing off of the leaves of cosmic plants.",
    "jei.cosmicsafari.rocket_jei": "The rocket is the key to adding creatures to your zoo! Simply add some rocket fuel, then give it a redstone signal. Give it some time, and when it returns, it may bring back DNA!"
